    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="0x00-如何Python工作路径：-切换到blog路径"><a href="#0x00-如何Python工作路径：-切换到blog路径" class="headerlink" title="0x00 如何Python工作路径： 切换到blog路径"></a>0x00 如何<code>Python</code>工作路径： 切换到<code>blog</code>路径</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> os <br>os.chdir(blogPath) <span class="hljs-comment"># 博客目录</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="0x01-一些命令的封装"><a href="#0x01-一些命令的封装" class="headerlink" title="0x01  一些命令的封装"></a>0x01  一些命令的封装</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 博客的命令 可以去官网查看</span><br>blogGen = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo g -d&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 更新本地缓存的命令</span><br>blogPush= <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo d&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 推送博客到github上的命令</span><br>blogShow = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo s&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 本地显示博客的命令</span><br>blogClean = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo clean&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 清理博客本地缓存的命令</span><br>blogNewOrgin = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo n &quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 新建一条博客的命令</span><br>blogPath = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;A:\Data\Blog\blog&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 博客地址</span><br>typoraPath = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;A:\Software\Typora\Typora&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># typora文件的地址</span><br>MDLocalPath = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;A:\Data\MarkDown&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 本地文件的地址</span><br>mdSourceDirPath = <span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;blogPath&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;os.sep&#125;</span>source<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;os.sep&#125;</span>_posts&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># 存放博客md数据的文件夹</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="0x02-创建新博客页面思路"><a href="#0x02-创建新博客页面思路" class="headerlink" title="0x02  创建新博客页面思路"></a>0x02  创建新博客页面思路</h2><pre><code class=" mermaid">flowchart TBopen[用typora打开该文件,上传图片]End(结束)Start(开始) --&gt;B[输入文件名 不含md]--&gt; c&#123;本地文件存在该文件&#125;c--&gt;|存在| g[将存在的数据粘贴到该文件] --&gt; openc--&gt; |不存在| openopen --&gt; End(结束)</code></pre><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> os<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> subprocess<br><br>blogGen = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo g -d&quot;</span><br>blogPush= <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo d&quot;</span><br>blogShow = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo s&quot;</span><br>blogClean = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo clean&quot;</span><br>blogNewOrgin = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;hexo n &quot;</span><br>blogPath = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;A:\Data\Blog\blog&quot;</span><br>typoraPath = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;A:\Software\Typora\Typora&quot;</span><br>MDLocalPath = <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;A:\Data\MarkDown&quot;</span><br><br>mdSourceDirPath = <span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;blogPath&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;os.sep&#125;</span>source<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;os.sep&#125;</span>_posts&quot;</span><br>os.chdir(blogPath)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span>():<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">commandResult</span>(<span class="hljs-params">command:<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    让Python 运行本地命令</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br>    result = subprocess.run(command, shell=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>, capture_output=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>, text=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;INFO&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> result.stdout:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;result：&quot;</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(result.stdout)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> E:<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(command)<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(E)<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 判断是否</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">isInSourceFile</span>(<span class="hljs-params">fileName:<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    判断你是不是已经创建过了</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br>    files = os.listdir(mdSourceDirPath)<br>    fileName = fileName+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.md&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> fileName <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> files:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">True</span> <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">False</span><br>    <br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span>  <span class="hljs-title function_">IsHaveLocalCopy</span>(<span class="hljs-params">MDLocalPath,name</span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    判断本地文件是否存在</span><br><span class="hljs-string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br>    localCopyPath = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> root, directories, files <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> os.walk(MDLocalPath):<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> file <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> files:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> name == file:<br>                localCopyPath = os.path.join(root, file)<br>                <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(localCopyPath)<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> localCopyPath    <br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span>():<br>    title= <span class="hljs-string">r&quot;重启&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>  <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> isInSourceFile(title):<br>        commandResult(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;blogNewOrgin&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;title&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)<br>    fileName = title +<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.md&quot;</span><br>    commandResult(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;typoraPath&#125;</span> <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;mdSourceDirPath&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;os.sep&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;fileName&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)<br>    <br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>  __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;__main__&#x27;</span>:<br>    title = <span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;创建文件名：&quot;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># title= r&quot;重启&quot;</span><br>    fileName = title +<span class="hljs-string">&quot;.md&quot;</span><br>    webFilePath = <span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;mdSourceDirPath&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;os.sep&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;fileName&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>  <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> isInSourceFile(title):<br>        commandResult(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;blogNewOrgin&#125;</span><span class="hljs-subst">&#123;title&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)<br>    <br><br>    localCopyPath = IsHaveLocalCopy(<span class="hljs-string">r&quot;A:\Data\MarkDown&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;重启.md&quot;</span>)<br>    allData = []<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span>  localCopyPath == <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(localCopyPath,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;r&quot;</span>,encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> F:<br>            allData = F.readlines()<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(webFilePath, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;a&quot;</span>,encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>)<span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> F2:<br>            F2.writelines(allData)<br>     <br><br>    commandResult(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;typoraPath&#125;</span> <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;webFilePath&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)<br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="打包"><a href="#打包" class="headerlink" title="打包"></a>打包</h2><p>使用 pyinstaller 打包</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmd">pyinstaller  fileName.py<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
